channel.title: Comments on: Dogpatch Labs coming to Ireland

item.title: By: Graham Carrick
item.dc:creator: Graham Carrick
item.description: Sounds like a very interesting concept and something that would be very welcome in Dublin. A step in the right direction by Enterprise Ireland in helping to create Ireland new knowledge economy. Will we see something similar to the San Fran operation in Dublin any time soon?

item.title: By: Ed Byrne
item.dc:creator: Ed Byrne
item.description: Another startup incubator for Ireland - jeepers really is feast or famine! Great though ... starting to become a hub here ... couple more high quality events and IE/Dublin will be European Tech Hub.
